de.bpmnaftool.model.bpmn.flowobject.FlowObject

Packages that use FlowObject
de.bpmnaftool.model.bpmn Representation of an BPMN model to construct, store and retrieve all model elements 
de.bpmnaftool.model.bpmn.connectingobject Package for ConnectingObjects, contains interfaces and classes for MessageFlows or SequenceFlows 
de.bpmnaftool.model.bpmn.flowobject Package for FlowObjects, contains interfaces and classes for Activities, Events and Gateways 
de.bpmnaftool.model.transformation Package for model transformation, contains interfaces and classes related to the transformation from AristaFlow to BPMN

Subinterfaces of FlowObject in de.bpmnaftool.model.bpmn.flowobject
 interface Activity
          The Activity object represents an activity of a BMPN model.
 interface Event
          An Event is a FlowObject which can be triggered for various reasons (see trigger attribute).
 interface Gateway
          A Gateway is a FlowObject which is used to specify the outgoing SequeceFlow, therefore it may have more than one outgoing SequenceFlow.
